
Enigma is a puzzle game. When the game starts there will be a riddle
displayed at the top of a board. The answer to each riddle is a number.
You enter the number you choose in the panel at the bottom of the screen.
Then click enter. If you don't click enter the game will not register your answer.
There are eight riddles in a round and you will have 3 Hearts.
To win you must answer most riddles correctly without losing all your hearts.
Your score will be displayed at the end of the round.
Please enter a name before you click start.

